flowchart TD
    A[Browse Available Properties] --> B[View Property Details]
    B --> C[Click 'Analyze Reuse Potential']
    C --> D{Logged In?}
    D -->|No| E[Quick Sign Up / Log In]
    D -->|Yes| F[Input Property Info or Select from Map]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Choose Reuse Type]
    G --> H{Reuse Option Selected?}
    H -->|Convert to Housing| I[View Zoning and Feasibility Data]
    H -->|Create Co-working Space| J[Analyze Market Demand + Utilities]
    H -->|Community Center| K[View Neighborhood Demographics + Needs]
    I --> L[Generate Reuse Report]
    J --> L
    K --> L
    L --> M[Add Notes or Questions]
    M --> N[Submit for Review or Policy Insight]
    N --> O[Confirmation Sent]
    O --> P[Track Project Impact / Updates]
